Help centre
This help centre contains answers to some common questions we often get asked, as well as a glossary of terms that are used on our website and in our literature, to help you with any queries you may have.


If the information or glossary term you require is not included below, please contact our Customer Relations team on 0800 390 390*, or email us at info@mandg.co.uk**
*Telephone calls may be recorded. 
**Please note, information in an email cannot be guaranteed as secure. We advise that you do not include any sensitive information when corresponding with M&G in this way.



