            Leading the way in Institutional Fixed Income


Find out about our fixed income capabilities 




















Our mutual funds capabilities
With more than £80.7 billion (€112.0 bilion; $119.8 bilion)* of client money in mutual funds, M&G is one of the largest active investors in the UK stock market. *As at 31 March 2015
Our mutual funds capabilities




Our fixed income capabilities
M&G is one of Europe's largest bond investors with fixed income assets exceeding £168bn (€196bn; US$207bn)* spanning the full range of public and private debt, as well as infrastructure.*As at 31 December 2016.
Our fixed income capabilities




Our real estate capabilities
M&G’s property fund management arm is M&G Real Estate. With £26.3bn (€30.8bn; US$32.5bn)* of assets, M&G Real Estate is one of the world’s largest property investors.  *As at 31 December 2016.
Our real estate capabilities

























